@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram - BPO Management System

[*] --> Search

state Search
Search : entry / Get the filter category
Search : do / Validate the filter category
Search : exit / Valid or Invalid filter category

Search --> [*] : [Invalid filter category]

Search --> SelectPriceRange : [Valid filter category]

state SelectPriceRange
SelectPriceRange : entry / Get the price range
SelectPriceRange : do / Validate the price range
SelectPriceRange : exit / Valid or Invalid price range

SelectPriceRange --> [*] : [Invalid price range]

SelectPriceRange --> DisplayResults : [Valid price range]

state DisplayResults
DisplayResults : entry / Get the matching users
DisplayResults : do / Display the matching users
DisplayResults : exit / Displayed matching users

DisplayResults --> [*]

@enduml
